Package view.renderEngine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityRenderer
    Delegate renderer to handle the rendering of entities.
    GuiRenderer
    The GuiRender is different from the other renderer classes, as it only needs to handle the rendering of 2D images.
    MasterRenderer
    Master renderer handles all delegations to the individual render class.
    SkyboxRenderer
    Delegate renderer to handle the rendering of the world's skybox

    A skybox is a cube of png images wrapped around the players position in the game world to simulate the feeling of a sky.
    TerrainRenderer
    Delegate renderer to handle the rendering of terrains.
